Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:21.71,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,んーあぁ　次の町まだ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.71,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,まだかなりある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.48,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今日中に到着するのは厳しいだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:30.57,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,また野宿〜？　もう〜！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:32.40,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,何とか　なんねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,少し戻ることになるが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:41.61,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,「レスタルゴ」で宿をとるか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:42.62,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,まじ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:45.39,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,やったー！話わかる〜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ったく　甘ぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.13,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,急速も必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:09.49,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ニャーハ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:10.59,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,最高〜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.59,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,部屋とれて　よかったな～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:13.97,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.06,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:17.13,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,出店見に行こうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:18.02,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ケバブ食おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:19.35,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,へぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:21.34,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あ　二人は？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:23.08,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,俺は残るかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.48,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,市場で食材を調達する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:26.87,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,先に行っていいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:28.23,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,オケー!　行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:30.02,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,早めに戻れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:33.89,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,どっから行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:36.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ケバブ一択
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:41.75,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,オネーさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.10,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,何食べてるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:43.64,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.01,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,お待たせ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:46.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,だれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.93,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,えぇ　あっ　えぇっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.31,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,そこで売ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:51.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ジャーね！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:53.79,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,じゃねぇ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.06,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ナツメグとシナモン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,それと、ブラックペッパーを２袋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:04.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,アイヨ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:08.97,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,そのままでもいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:10.66,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ジャムにしてもウマイヨ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ではこれも頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.27,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,何作ってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:20.74,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,おっ　「いつものやつ」か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今回はバナナで試してみる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:25.03,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,よくやるねぇ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:27.10,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,なんで何度も作ってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,まぁな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.46,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,良い色だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.46,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,キッチンをお借りしています
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.12,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いいよ　いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.28,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,甘い物ばかり作ってるが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.28,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,そんなに好きなのか？イグニス
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:49.75,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:50.80,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.25,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,お疲れ様です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:53.05,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ハァー！明日いきなり数学か〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:55.92,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,やばいっつぅが全部やばいよ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.41,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ノクト余裕じゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.47,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,俺、王子だから内申関係ねーし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,じゃなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.95,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,王子！テスト無くしてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.35,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,邪魔しているぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.40,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,axa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.40,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.80,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,野菜ばっか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.51,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,偏った食事ばかり　とっているようだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.94,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,栄養バランスを考えて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.33,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,たまには自炊を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.37,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,はい　はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.91,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,夕食にするから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.91,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,手洗い　うがいを済ませてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.79,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,んー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.64,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,漫画なら棚に収めた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.47,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ルナフレーナ様の手帳は引き出しだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.59,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,返事をするなら早い方いい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.80,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,分かってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.56,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ボタンが落ちていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.08,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あれは？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:52.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あぁ　制服のやつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.26,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,帰ってつけるから　出しておいてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:02.67,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ふぁ〜　食い過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.51,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,デザートは入るか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:08.96,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今回は蜂蜜の種類を変えてみた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.55,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,おぉ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.86,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.59,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ふんー　違うかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:19.79,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,もっと甘かったし、サクサクしてた気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:20.84,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.21,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,パイ生地の方も試作が必要か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.58,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,でもウマイよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.92,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,イグニスも食わね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.48,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あぁ　コーヒーは？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.80,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,うん　サンキュ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.40,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,試験勉強があるだろうから帰るが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.40,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,前にも言ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.83,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,外出時には戸締りに気をつけてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.97,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,玄関だけでは不十分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.08,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,んー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.10,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,それとゴミの分別も頑張ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.60,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,それ以前に部屋に放置するな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.70,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,誰かがやってくると思ったら大間違いだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:53.69,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,んー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:54.81,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ノクト！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:55.84,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,はい　はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.62,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,きちんとしてくれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.40,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,一人暮らしは取り止めになるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.16,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,それと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,国勢レポートだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.41,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,詳しくはまた説明するが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.82,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,目を通しておいてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.96,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,テスト終わってからでいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:13.53,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,試験が大事なのは当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.96,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,だが　お前は「次期」国王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.96,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,その自覚を持ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,げぇ〜　ノクト勉強してる！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.82,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,何食ってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.24,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,朝飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.53,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いる？　いらないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.13,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,一口だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.60,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,うまい〜！　これ何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:43.71,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,知らね〜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.97,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,昔、　ちょっとテネブラエに居ったことあったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.77,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,そん時食べったおやつがすげー甘かったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.21,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,どんなんだったかあんま覚えてねーだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.30,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,イグニスに言ったら再現しようとしてくれてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.38,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,たまに作ってくれんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.13,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,でも　なんかいつも違うんだよなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.68,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,こんなにうまいのに？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.88,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ていうかあの人お菓子作るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.84,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,帝国の動きが活発になってきております
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.43,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ルシスに攻め込んでくるのは時間の問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.10,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,「魔法障壁」が　要となりましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:23.28,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,帝国軍はまだしばらく兵力増強に徹しているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,先日のガラード区域への襲撃は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,恐らく「新型兵器」の性能を試したのだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.60,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,報告ではこちらの「魔法の力」が阻害されたと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.75,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,奴ら「障壁」を破壊つもりか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.88,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今はこちらも予想を見る他ないが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.20,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,警戒態勢をとるよう通達せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.20,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,以上　解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.05,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,イグニス
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.77,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.38,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ノクトはどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.51,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,本日より期末試験です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.33,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,勉強するように言いましたが　なんとも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:04.72,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,一人暮らしは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.80,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,食事の偏りが気になりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.80,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,指導すれば改善するかと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.48,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いつも　すまんな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:11.40,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.29,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,「魔法障壁」の影響ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:16.89,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,だろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,「障壁」を張り
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.66,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,民を守ってこそ王だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.02,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,私が居なくなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.16,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,次の「ルシスの血」が継ぐことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:36.20,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,だが　その前に、なんとしてでも　この戦争を終わらせる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.54,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ノクトを頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.55,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.00,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あぁ〜　終わった　おわった〜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.12,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,おい　明日まだあるだろう　テスト
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.28,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,一日で十分だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.85,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あっ　陛下だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.47,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.70,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あれ？　陛下って　足悪かったっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.88,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,, 遅かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.59,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,試験は午前中じゃなかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.27,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,グーセン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.98,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,明日の科目の勉強は？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.73,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今日は何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.97,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ワイシャツのボタンを付けたから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.02,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,届けに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.46,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,それと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.50,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,昨日を渡したレポートを読んだか?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:52.92,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.24,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,だろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.30,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,読んだ形跡がなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.24,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,帝国との大規模の戦争は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.50,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,３０年前に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.13,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,一時収束したが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.13,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いまだ　予断を許さない状況だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.61,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,報道規制されているが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.84,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,現に小規模な衝突は時折起こっている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.42,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,わかってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.69,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ルシス１５０年の平和は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.22,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,代々「王の力」によって　創られる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.06,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,「魔法障壁」のおかげだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.65,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,王は多大な力を消費し
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,その「代償」を全て御身に引き受けられる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:30.41,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,レギス様はしばらく前戦に出ず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.53,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,「魔法障壁」に集中すると仰っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.04,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,もう　ほとんど　「武器召喚」はできないらし出来ないらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.34,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,聞いているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.73,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,それ今聞かなきゃいけねーこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.57,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,では　いつ聞くんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.56,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,言っただろう　お前は　「時期」国王なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:48.38,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いずれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.03,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,親父が死ぬって？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.80,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,そうは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.08,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,言ってんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.41,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,俺が王になるのは親父が死ぬ時だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.43,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,落ち着け　ただ事実を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.93,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,事実って何だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.14,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,話にならないな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.84,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,だが　考えておいてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.13,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:40.16,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？テスト出来なかったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.75,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,お前らどこの学校だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.28,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ヒエー！　今も　帰るところで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.09,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,グラディオ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.56,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,イリスは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.27,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,まだ学校か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.10,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,最近稽古サボってっからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.52,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,抜き打ちテスト
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.14,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,集中しろ！ノクト！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.92,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,うっせぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.55,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,おいおい　陛下が嘆くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.20,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,そんなんじゃ　国を任せられないな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.92,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,分かってんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.10,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,わかってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.41,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.86,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今のままじゃダメだって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.67,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:41.47,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,親父が死ぬなんて　考えたくねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.08,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ノクトのやつ　ちょっとなまっただぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.20,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,お前のところに来たのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.58,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,この前な
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.59,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,また　稽古サボりそうだったら　連れて来い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.11,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:22.72,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:26.84,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いや　ノクトが何を考えているのか　分からなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.41,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,自分の立場分かっているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,お前が思ったより考えているぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.26,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:58.69,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.56,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,なにか燃やしたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.01,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,料理　したのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:39.50,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,まぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.90,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,腹　減らねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.36,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,わ　悪いが　今日はなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.17,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,たまに食べるとうまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:08.73,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あのさ　フライパンって燃えないゴミ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.85,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ああ　あれはまだ使える
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.96,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今度コゲ落としを持ってこよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.73,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,このあいだは　言い過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.56,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,この前のは美味しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.38,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,あ　かしか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.74,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,食べたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.67,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,また作ったら食べる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.26,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,たっだいまー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:48.08,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,おぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.79,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いい匂い！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.84,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,何作ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:55.64,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,食べるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.72,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,お　ほほー　これ　久しぶり〜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.32,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,いっただきまーす！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.54,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,今回の　なに味これ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.54,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,うん　おいしぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:11.05,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.09,Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro,,0,0,0,,ちがう
